snippet.title: The Dead Await: Prologue - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The Dead Await: Prologue is a deckbuilding survival RPG set during a zombie apocalypse. Build your deck, craft, and try to survive. The Dead Await: Prologue is available now on PC.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
